<p>Add new photos every week. Fresh photos signal an active business to Google. Read our <a href="/blog/gbp-photos-guide/">GBP photos guide</a> for the full strategy.</p>
<h3>Post Weekly Updates</h3>
<p>Google Business Profile posts keep your listing active and give you more real estate in search results. Post at least once per week.</p>
<p>Post ideas for trainers:</p>
<ul>
<li>Client success stories (anonymized or with permission)</li>
<li>Workout tips for the current season</li>
<li>Special offers or free consultation promos</li>
<li>Event announcements (boot camps, challenges, workshops)</li>
<li>Health and nutrition tips</li>
</ul>
<p>Each post should include a photo, a call to action, and relevant keywords. Our research on <a href="/blog/gbp-posting-frequency/">GBP posting frequency</a> shows that businesses posting weekly see 2x more profile interactions.</p>
